  <brief_title>An Observational Study of Avastin in First Line in Elderly Patients With Metastatic Colorectal Cancer (CASSIOPEE)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non Interventional Study Evaluating Efficacy and Safety in a Cohort of Elderly Patients of First Line Therapy With Avastin Â® Regimen for Metastatic Colorectal Cancer.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Hoffmann-La Roche</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Hoffmann-La Roche</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This multicenter, prospective, observational study will evaluate the efficacy and safety of
      Avastin (bevacizumab) in first-line therapy in elderly patients with metastatic colorectal
      cancer. Data will be collected from eligible patients for24 months.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
